msgid "why-use-istio"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/faq/general/why-use-istio.rst:4
msgid ""
"Traditionally, much of the logic handled by Istio has been built directly"
" into applications. Across a fleet of services, managing updates to this "
"communications logic can be a large burden. Istio provides an "
"infrastructure-level solution to managing service communications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/faq/general/why-use-istio.rst:9
msgid ""
"*Application developers*: With Istio managing how traffic flows across "
"their services, developers can focus exclusively on business logic and "
"iterate quickly on new features."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/faq/general/why-use-istio.rst:13
msgid ""
"*Service operators*: Istio enables policy enforcement and mesh monitoring"
" from a single centralized control point, independent of application "
"evolution. As a result, operators can ensure continuous policy compliance"
" through a simplified management plane."
msgstr ""

